<h2 style="font-weight:bold">Workshops</h2>
<br>
<p style="font-size:11pt;margin-bottom:15px">
    <strong>Development Workshops</strong> run for 10 weeks and allow you to have taster sessions on meditation, 
    spiritual healing, clairvoyance, psychometry, and transfiguration. 
    The courses are led by trained mediums and offer an interesting insight into the world of Spiritualism. 
    If you are interested please <a href="/Default.swg?link=Contact">contact us.</a>
    We will add your details to our waiting list and contact you once we are ready to begin our next class. Before the class you will be asked along for a chat to ascertain whether this is the right path for you at this moment. You will also be given further details regarding the commitment required in terms of time and costs.
</p>

<p>
