</p>

<p style="font-size:11pt;margin-bottom:15px">
    <strong>Introduction to Clairvoyance/Advanced Clairvoyance</strong>  classes run every Monday and Thursday evening from 7pm and allow members to develop skills learned in the development workshop. Many of our members go on to be platform mediums, working in Church on a Sunday or at our demonstration evenings to raise funds for our charity    </p>
